description: This file defines a Next.js page component for displaying details of a specific note, including static parameter generation for routing. It contains functions to generate static params and a React component that renders note details and UI elements, currently as placeholders with disabled inputs and buttons.

methods.name: generateStaticParams
methods.description: Provides a set of placeholder IDs to enable static generation of note detail pages.

methods.name: NoteDetailsPage
methods.description: Main React component that renders the note details page with placeholder values.
